134
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:09,400
Epstein, in der amerikanischen
High Society.

135
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:14,120
JL: Absolut.

136
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:17,080
Bill Gates, die Clintons,
Dutzende Dokumente,

137
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:19,280
